data_table.description: The dataset represents variables used to collect information about CNS functions, e.g. cognitive and motor functions, including memory, attention, arithmetic, verbal abilities, tactile abilities, and motor coordination. Data were collected at baseline, years 2, 5, 7 and close-out (see also pht000265, form 13).
